                        Guilford township, when only two days old, weighed <emph rend="italic">One
                            hundred and seventeen pounds</emph>!--Well, if that don't take the
                        Premium at our next Fair, we'll knock under. Guilford can't be beaten.
                        That's so.</p>
                </transcript>
